OL,4,CAfghanistan: Leaked document warns of
OL,5,Crefugee funding shortfall
OL,6, The Treasury must "urgently" confirm
OL,7, extra funding before councils can start
OL,8, making offers to house Afghan refugees,
OL,9, a document seen by the BBC suggests.
OL,11,FIt estimates the cost of helping those
OL,12,Fcoming to the UK over the next 10 years
OL,13,Fcould be more than #2.5bn.
OL,15,FAnd it suggests a shortfall in the cash
OL,16,Fcommitted by Whitehall so far.
OL,18,FA government spokesperson said hundreds
OL,19,Fof Afghan nationals who had worked
OL,20,Falongside the British in Afghanistan
OL,21,Fhad already been welcomed to the UK.
